rows.label: tlk70000002_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Most products in front of
Obibi's shop burned to crisp...

rows.label: tlk70000002_02_msg0002
rows.name:
And products from inside not popular
with Nopon... But on other wing, liked
by Chamber of Commerce workers.

rows.label: tlk70000002_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Feel truly thankful when Obibi
think about those people.

rows.label: tlk70000002_02_msg0004
rows.name:
But Obibi not happy about having
to start from scratch like that...

rows.label: tlk70000002_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Meh? No, Obibi not scratch because
of fleas! Be serious!

rows.label: tlk70000002_02_msg0006
rows.name:
By way! The product in warehouse
should still be fine!

rows.label: tlk70000002_02_msg0007
rows.name:
Obibi will keep trying
best to grow business!
